QUESTION LINK:-
https://www.hackerrank.com/challenges/weather-observation-station-5/problem?isFullScreen=true

SOLUTION:-

SELECT CITY, LENGTH(CITY) AS length
FROM STATION
ORDER BY length ASC, CITY ASC
LIMIT 1;

SELECT CITY, LENGTH(CITY) AS length
FROM STATION
ORDER BY length DESC, CITY ASC
LIMIT 1;
